## 📌 Milestone 1: Project Setup & Problem Understanding

### 🎯 Objective
Understand the business problem and set up the foundation for the IT Support Ticket Analysis project.

### 📊 Business Problem
IT support teams face challenges such as:
- High volume of unresolved tickets
- SLA (Service Level Agreement) violations
- Lack of visibility into ticket priority and resolution trends
- Inefficient resource allocation

### 📁 Dataset Overview
- Source: Internal / Simulated IT Ticket Data
- Key Columns:
  - Ticket ID
  - Issue Type
  - Priority
  - Status
  - Created Date
  - Resolved Date
  - Assigned Team

### 🛠️ Tools & Technologies
- Python (Pandas, NumPy)
- Power BI
- Excel (for quick validation)

### ⚙️ Tasks Completed
- Defined project scope and objectives
- Imported dataset
- Understood data structure and features
- Identified key KPIs:
  - Ticket Volume
  - Resolution Time
  - SLA Compliance
  - Priority Distribution

### ✅ Outcome
Clear understanding of the problem and data structure, ready for data cleaning and preprocessing.
